data.description: 2 lots plus a Clayton mobile home included in this price.  Nestled in the secure & gated community of Holiday Villages of Medina, this beautifully maintained 3-bd, 2-bath Clayton mobile home is an opportunity you won't want to miss. As you step inside, you'll discover a thoughtfully designed open floor plan with split bedrooms. The living area is inviting and perfect for gatherings. A highlight of this property is the deck, where you can enjoy your favorite beverage. Residents of Holiday Villages enjoy a host of amenities for their pleasure.  While Lake Medina, available to owners, is experiencing lower water levels due to drought, it's a fantastic recreational resource at its full potential. This property presents an excellent opportunity to live in a secure and friendly community.
